<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="division-n">division <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'vɪʒn/    美 /dɪ'vɪʒn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] &amp; [C] [单数] 分；分开；分配：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In groups discuss what the possible work <strong>division</strong> was <strong>between</strong> men <strong>and</strong> women. 
分组讨论以前的男女分工可能是什么样的。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 5</footer></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 分界线；部分；部门：</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3-u">3.★ <strong>[U] 除 (法)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>30 divided by 5 is a simple division. 
30除以5是一个简单的除法。</p></div>

<h4 id="4-c-u">4.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 分裂；分歧；差异：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Division</strong> of opinion <strong>among</strong> themselves contributed to their defeat. 
他们之间的意见分歧导致了他们的失败。</p></div></div>